import { Card, CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter, Box, Center, Heading, Button } from '@chakra-ui/react'

export default function App() {
    return (
        <Box position="relative" h="100vh" p={12}>
            <Center>
                <Card >
                    <CardBody>
                        Hiking is a long, vigorous walk, usually on trails or footpaths in the
                        countryside. Walking for pleasure developed in Europe during the
                        eighteenth century.
                    </CardBody>
                    <CardFooter>
                        <Button colorScheme="blue">Sign up</Button>
                    </CardFooter>
                </Card>
            </Center>
        </Box>
    );
}
